ion of the conversation. This added an element of fun to the program while building conversation skills.","The feature set was well organized and offered a variety of applications, including a convenient feature which allows you to select the area of language acquisition you would like to study. The game section, however, could use improvement; the only games offered were Go Fish and a crossword puzzle. With the addition of a few more games this program would be far more fun to use.","Also, Learn to Speak Spanish did not come with a headset. This is a standard feature included in most language software packages and should be included with the program."]},"id":"9f045810-d61f-4f13-97da-c0f4695108a4","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Learning Versatility"},"id":"9bd6a364-5a5a-458d-be60-fdcc85608f73","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The software navigation is well designed-intuitive and straightforward. You begin with basics for beginners then move on to the language essentials segment, including pronunciation and basic vocabulary. The flow of the program is natural, not choppy."]},"id":"c2053356-37e7-48b5-ad96-33a659a0a413","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Teaching Tools"},"id":"09fcac43-f301-486a-99cb-4204ceb7faf5","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The installation was simple except when we attempted to set up the speech recognition portion of the program. The program crashed with each attempt to apply this feature and often crashed the entire computer."]},"id":"129a9cd7-2139-4709-87f4-a58fd0a380b7","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"ee9fe3d0-4f16-451c-bb14-0d984e7a2151","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This program is a fair choice for the beginning to intermediate level Spanish speaker. Learn to Speak Essentials teaches the fundamentals of language acquisition well. With some improvements, this program would rank higher in our book."]},"id":"d7d6e79f-0f34-4728-a96a-fa2244c3dddb","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_rev